The list.

03:05.251 --> 03:07.352
I can't believe
I'm not on here.

03:07.353 --> 03:09.487
How could I lose
"best eyebrows"
to joey pagoonis?

03:09.488 --> 03:11.455
He only has one.

03:15.060 --> 03:17.161
Hi, guys.
Hi, mom.

03:20.532 --> 03:22.467
Why are you
standing like that?

03:22.468 --> 03:25.603
