a work of art.

03:28.541 --> 03:31.409
Do you think the kids
are getting weirder?

03:31.410 --> 03:35.347
They've moved way past weird.
They're into that
frightening category now.

03:35.348 --> 03:38.116
Wait till I tell you
about what I found out
at school today.

03:38.117 --> 03:40.218
You know my friend patty?

03:40.219 --> 03:42.820
That woman you like
'cause she's older
than you?

03:42.821 --> 03:46.157
Yeah. Get a load of this.
She's pregnant.

03:46.158 --> 03:48.059
That's great.

03:48.060 --> 03:50.594
