some precautions.

04:00.372 --> 04:05.043
They were using precautions.
The same kind we use.

04:05.044 --> 04:06.711
<i>(grunts)</i> oh, no.

04:08.481 --> 04:11.716
I wouldn't want to find
myself in that boat.

04:11.717 --> 04:13.952
