the tube-tying thing.

04:53.158 --> 04:57.762
Well, I am talking about
the tube-tying thing,
except it's your tubes.

04:57.763 --> 05:01.533
You can back up
that clip ship right now.

05:01.534 --> 05:04.935
Honey, it is much safer
for a man to get a vasectomy

05:04.936 --> 05:07.538
