invasive.

05:34.833 --> 05:38.469
My gynecologist
gave me the name
of a very good urologist.

05:38.470 --> 05:41.272
Can we just go talk
to this dr. Kaplan?

05:41.273 --> 05:44.942
Why are we slamming the door
on having more kids, anyway?

05:47.479 --> 05:49.848
