frightening weirdoes.

05:52.051 --> 05:55.754
I said it
in a very positive light.
I love those little guys.

05:55.755 --> 05:59.023
Hey, kids, get down here!
Daddy wants to tell you
how much he loves you!

06:03.696 --> 06:05.997
Hey, guys.
Hey, marty.

06:05.998 --> 06:07.999
Hey, benny.
Hey, marty.

06:09.568 --> 06:11.536
